A man died after he was hit by a train at the Florida Train station in Florida, west of Johannesburg on Wednesday.It is believed that the incident happened at around 8:00am on Wednesday morning the deceased is suspected to be in his in 20s.On arrival ER24 paramedics found the man lying on the side of the tracks,It is alleged that the deceased fell between the platform and an oncoming train.Unfortunately the man give in to his multiple injuries and was declared dead on the scene.Local authorities were on the scene to begin their investigations.-TNA Reporter 